To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private Counterattack _counterattack;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_counterattack = Counterattack(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_counterattack.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "counterattack", _counterattack.Current.Value);
}
# In Initialize()
symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.counterattack = self.Counterattack(symbol)

# In OnData()
if self.counterattack.IsReady:
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "counterattack", self.counterattack.Current.Value)
